        The information provided on this site is designed to support, not replace, the relationship that exists between a patient/site visitor and his/her existing physician. The material on this website was written to provide a way to help the user track his/her food and symptoms associated with Food Allergies and Gastrointestinal Disorders. All of the material written on the blog/website and all of its articles are the opinions of our own. The authors and Sneezy T disclaim any responsibility for any adverse effects resulting from the information presented on this website. The information enclosed is not designed to take the place of a doctor's instructions. People using the Sneezy T website/blog are urged to contact a doctor for specific information regarding guidelines for care.
